headline: Morgan Stanley Maintains An Equal Weight Rating On The Travelers Companies, Inc. (TRV)
summary: The Travelers Companies, Inc. (NYSE:TRV) is among the 12 Best Performing Dow Stocks in 2025. According to The Fly on November 17, 2025, Morgan Stanley lifted its price objective for The Travelers Companies, Inc. (NYSE:TRV) from $285 to $295 and retained its Equal Weight rating. Following Q3 results, analyst Bob Huang updated the company’s insurance-sector […]
